README ME FIRST

Fuwo is a PHP application that needs a database to run on.
Currently tested MariaDB and MySQL.

INSTALL

Fuwo needs a database connection.
Use the script called fuwo_db.sql from the INSTALL directoy to create a fuwo database. Script is tested o  MariaDB.

SETUP

FuWo stores the connection information to the database in the following file in the root directory: databaseConnectionProperties.xxxx
Enter your connection details there and rename the file from "databaseConnectionProperties.xxxx" to "databaseConnectionProperties.conf"
